The paper deals with coding and decoding techniques for a relay protocol in a communication system, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of decision rules and equalizers, which are topics in control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper analyzes the performance of the protocol, which is related to communication systems (cs.COMM).
